i><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>setDate()</strong></code> 方法根据本地时间来指定一个日期对象的天数。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/date-setdate.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>dateObj</var>.setDate(<em>dayValue</em>)</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"dayvalue\"><code>dayValue</code></dt>\n <dd>一个整数，表示该月的第几天。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>如果 <code>dayValue</code>&nbsp;超出了月份的合理范围，<code>setDate</code>&nbsp;将会相应地更新&nbsp;<code>Date</code> 对象。</p>\n\n<p>例如，如果为&nbsp;<code>dayValue</code> 指定 0，那么日期就会被设置为上个月的最后一天。</p>\n\n<p>如果 dayValue 被设置为负数，日期会设置为上个月最后一天往前数这个负数绝对值天数后的日期。-1 会设置为上月最后一天的前一天（译者注：例如当前为 4 月，如果 setDate(-2),则为 3 月 29 日）</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_using_setdate","title":"例子：使用<code>setDate</code>方法","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> theBigDay <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1962</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1962-07-07</span>\ntheBigDay<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setDate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">24</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 1962-07-24</span>\ntheBigDay<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setDate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">32</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 1962-08-01</span></code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"例子：使用setDate方法"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范版本</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">注解</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>ECMAScript 1st Edition. Implemented in JavaScript 1.0</td>\n   <td>Standard</td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.9.5.36\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Date.prototype.setDate</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-date.prototype.setdate\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Date.prototype.setDate</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"bro